---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Kaya Blue — architects of high-performance digital experiences">
<main class="aura-glow">
<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-20 py-24 md:py-32">
<div class="max-w-3xl">
<p class="font-mono text-accent tracking-widest text-xs mb-4 uppercase font-bold">EXPERTISE &amp; LEGACY</p>
<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white tracking-tight leading-none mb-6">About Kaya Blue</h1>
<p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-text-muted font-medium">Crafting Digital Excellence</p>
</div>
</section>
<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-20 pb-24">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6">
<div class="md:col-span-8 bg-card-dark rounded-xl p-10 relative overflow-hidden group border border-slate-800 hover:border-accent/50 transition-all">
<div class="relative z-10">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent mb-6 text-4xl">rocket_launch</span>
<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 tracking-tight text-white">Our Mission</h2>
<p class="text-lg text-text-muted leading-relaxed font-medium">
At Kaya Blue, we believe the digital frontier is the canvas for modern legacies. Our mission is to engineer high-performance systems that don't just exist online but dominate their respective markets. We combine architectural precision with creative intuition to transform complex business challenges into seamless digital experiences.
</p>
</div>
<div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-5 text-accent">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-9xl">architecture</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="md:col-span-4 flex flex-col gap-6">
<div class="bg-card-dark rounded-xl p-8 flex-1 border border-slate-800 hover:border-accent/50 transition-all">
<p class="font-mono text-accent text-xs mb-6 tracking-widest uppercase font-bold">CORE VALUES</p>
<ul class="space-y-8">
<li class="flex items-start gap-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent">auto_awesome</span>
<div><h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1 text-white">Innovation</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted font-medium">Pushing the boundaries of what is technically possible.</p></div>
</li>
<li class="flex items-start gap-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent">biotech</span>
<div><h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1 text-white">Precision</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted font-medium">Meticulous attention to every line of code and pixel.</p></div>
</li>
<li class="flex items-start gap-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent">bolt</span>
<div><h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1 text-white">Impact</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted font-medium">Driving measurable growth and digital authority.</p></div>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="bg-[#0d1b2a] py-24 px-6 lg:px-20 border-y border-slate-800">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
<div class="text-center mb-16">
<p class="font-mono text-accent text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 font-bold">METHODOLOGY</p>
<h2 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">Our Approach</h2>
<div class="h-1 w-20 bg-accent mx-auto mt-6 rounded-full"></div>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
<div class="relative p-8 rounded-xl bg-card-dark border-l-4 border-accent shadow-xl border-y border-r border-slate-800">
<div class="text-6xl font-black text-accent/10 absolute top-4 right-4 font-mono">01</div>
<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight text-white">Discovery</h3>
<p class="text-text-muted font-medium leading-relaxed">Deep immersion into your business ecosystem to identify untapped opportunities and technical requirements.</p>
</div>
<div class="relative p-8 rounded-xl bg-card-dark border-l-4 border-accent shadow-xl border-y border-r border-slate-800">
<div class="text-6xl font-black text-accent/10 absolute top-4 right-4 font-mono">02</div>
<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight text-white">Design</h3>
<p class="text-text-muted font-medium leading-relaxed">Architecting visual systems that align with high-end brand identities and technical precision.</p>
</div>
<div class="relative p-8 rounded-xl bg-card-dark border-l-4 border-accent shadow-xl border-y border-r border-slate-800">
<div class="text-6xl font-black text-accent/10 absolute top-4 right-4 font-mono">03</div>
<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight text-white">Execution</h3>
<p class="text-text-muted font-medium leading-relaxed">Rigorous engineering and deployment of scalable solutions built for long-term performance.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-20 py-24">
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-16 gap-4">
<div>
<p class="font-mono text-accent text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 font-bold">THE ARCHITECTS</p>
<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-none text-white">Leadership</h2>
</div>
<p class="max-w-md text-text-muted font-medium leading-relaxed">Meet the visionary minds directing the future of technical prestige at Kaya Blue.</p>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
<div class="group">
<div class="aspect-[4/5] bg-card-dark rounded-xl mb-6 overflow-hidden relative border border-slate-800 shadow-lg">
<img alt="Elias Thorne" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 group-hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-500 opacity-90" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDKM4k556ksyq8E7eQEqUnDdbclTmzbLSH4j2MHzpL1OgAaGHqH8jVPKjx8c7pYRlUKQCIuvpHbQmcki1WaHQ54hh8rbI4yUcb3je8yxCg7tX7nsAgZnhag1EJ8fiHtwfs5uj8pE2WsQUG6yvSK0u3lnnHpw7qD_sgkqZvDJSGOTNqVrruLFDg34CmmiP6okfCvFp5qyq_-NaSXCYFhGiBk4nSvtbZJF-QglO4Rg-E3pJ7vZwh7ggIW47ngVrKkMc64Seu2V9aCqqQ" />
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary/80 to-transparent"></div>
</div>
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-white group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">Elias Thorne</h3>
<p class="text-accent font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mt-2 font-bold">Founder &amp; CEO</p>
</div>
<div class="group">
<div class="aspect-[4/5] bg-card-dark rounded-xl mb-6 overflow-hidden relative border border-slate-800 shadow-lg">
<img alt="Elena Vance" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 group-hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-500 opacity-90" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuA50LQbcXNOAS57qvw2sWo1HoEBz9cqV4n2TN0QIz29aT0IRBE0kzAYgMFxCIljWpbN3l1QXjeQU5NrV0QfSKAoSGmtw-BmOo4zal-AhZpEUDanvHYbRJzoYIgh3mlblwXWRVDQYsdkCbyRNKf53-2bFo0c6nQY862rXkhZpIluldvuqVTkEuiTPPtmcl9H2XozjlEq2i69s6UKLNOic4VjsYpDiKVzhgcfjZ6Hn-d8PA6ekd3RYuIH3hJy1ACE5JLWr0h4cHAWXL8" />
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary/80 to-transparent"></div>
</div>
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-white group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">Elena Vance</h3>
<p class="text-accent font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mt-2 font-bold">Chief Tech Officer</p>
</div>
<div class="group">
<div class="aspect-[4/5] bg-card-dark rounded-xl mb-6 overflow-hidden relative border border-slate-800 shadow-lg">
<img alt="Marcus Chen" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 group-hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-500 opacity-90" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAsAYdHzIW60_vJTrcfbV19OaPdkD7FKU959-ZEGwPSoI8zlJFrQTNS0f6jDdtEDoGLXyUJvsaY6zjHqfz_oK0ZU2gIX37ft2glLSWICKhwQbFRsnw51laFVjIZ-2uUkdgs-unKIi8F32nHKmVDHzxdr-unAdCioGHdvoIjbYpPT5EAzHWf-QYa3Qo8zHGTlZ_ZImB5bQVmVGhJaMsvk0eYWuhRZhWFfSXoD5YHY-12QQpio8Urf7T3kfyfEGgEqIGztDNTY07iCRE" />
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary/80 to-transparent"></div>
</div>
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-white group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">Marcus Chen</h3>
<p class="text-accent font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mt-2 font-bold">Design Director</p>
</div>
<div class="group">
<div class="aspect-[4/5] bg-card-dark rounded-xl mb-6 overflow-hidden relative border border-slate-800 shadow-lg">
<img alt="Sarah Jenkins" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 group-hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-500 opacity-90" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDgwA9aD5SOAHQDsEALcsDgoRN62JeB7LH6bf7aQkbMU1TCkaFiWfkCjwP0NDyhdCOLcwlPay-1WkiRQeP7z-YLblADpsHB1IHN8ADKUGZECZUjdjiy8uIh-Axvj6LsWpda2G4vgSW75oC2KnC6SYuKVTpVAUlNGnu0VT9O6TrJrDTbqyvlMB43F_fUNNmbjOxjWXc-xNcqw3lfe7oJBnjHfpLZiB4h82s8VOA6bXO2Px9ICJBLLjg3vU75oTjZI2b25wfWTJyotnA" />
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary/80 to-transparent"></div>
</div>
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-white group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">Sarah Jenkins</h3>
<p class="text-accent font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mt-2 font-bold">Head of Strategy</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-20 py-24">
<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-card-dark to-primary rounded-2xl p-12 lg:p-20 text-center border border-slate-800 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mr-20 -mt-20 w-64 h-64 bg-accent/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
<div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 -ml-20 -mb-20 w-64 h-64 bg-accent/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
<div class="relative z-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
<h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black tracking-tight mb-8 leading-none text-white">Ready to Build Your Legacy?</h2>
<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center">
<a href="/book-a-call" class="inline-block bg-accent text-primary px-10 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold hover:scale-105 transition-transform accent-glow text-lg">Start Your Project</a>
<a href="/our-work" class="inline-block border border-slate-700 text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-card-dark transition-all text-lg">View Portfolio</a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</main>
</BaseLayout>
